CONFIGURATION
-------------

Environment
- standard debian jessie installation
- open incoming port 25

Users
 - create a dedicated <mailuser>

Packets
 - exim4
 - cups
 - apache2 / php
 - php-mime-email-parser
 - wkthmltopdf
 - git

Clone Repository
git clone https://github.com/wagneral/ape.git


WORKFLOW
--------
Processing Mail
 - exim4 retriebves mails on incoming port 25 (!firewall restrictions)
   and redircets them all to the <mailuser> as specified in /etc/aliases

   *: <mailuser>

 - the 'mailuser' forwards incoming mail to the ape script as specified in
   /home/<mailuser>/.forward

   <mailuser>@servername.de,"|php -q /home/<mailuser>/ape/init.php"

Printing
 - the named script parses the mail and gathers the required information
   before printing via cups printserver